# ============================================
# MINIMIZE APP — ENVIRONMENT VARIABLES
# ============================================

# 1. SUPABASE (Database + Auth + Storage)
# Get these from: https://supabase.com → Your Project → Settings → API
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL=https://your-project.supabase.co
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=your-anon-key-here
SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY=your-service-role-key-here  # Keep secret! Never expose to frontend

# 2. REPLICATE (AI Image Generation)
# Get this from: https://replicate.com → Profile → API Tokens
# Create new token → Name: "Minimize" → Copy the token
# Model we're using: google/nano-banana (~$0.039 per image)
# Alternative models: lucataco/remove-bg, tstramer/midjourney-diffusion
REPLICATE_API_TOKEN=your-replicate-token-here

# 3. STRIPE (Payments — Optional for MVP)
# Get from: https://dashboard.stripe.com → Developers → API Keys
STRIPE_SECRET_KEY=sk_test_...
STRIPE_WEBHOOK_SECRET=whsec_...  # Get this after setting up webhook in Stripe Dashboard
NEXT_PUBLIC_STRIPE_PUBLISHABLE_KEY=pk_test_...
STRIPE_PRICE_ID_PRO=price_...  # Create a product in Stripe → Copy Price ID

# 4. APP CONFIG
NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_URL=http://localhost:3000  # Change to your domain when deployed

# ============================================
# HOW TO GET EACH KEY:
# ============================================
# 
# SUPABASE:
#   1. Go to https://supabase.com → Sign up (free)
#   2. Create new project
#   3. Project Settings → API → Copy URL and Anon Key
#   4. Project Settings → API → Copy Service Role Key (keep secret!)
#   5. Go to SQL Editor → Run everything in supabase/schema.sql
#   6. Storage → Create bucket "uploads" → Make public
#
# REPLICATE:
#   1. Go to https://replicate.com → Sign up (free, $5 credit)
#   2. Click profile (top right) → Settings → API Tokens
#   3. Create new token → Name: "Minimize" → Copy token
#   4. Model: google/nano-banana (best for image editing)
#   5. Cost: ~$0.039 per image generated
#
# STRIPE (Optional):
#   1. Go to https://stripe.com → Sign up
#   2. Dashboard → Developers → API Keys → Copy Secret and Publishable keys
#   3. Products → Create Product "Minimize Pro" → $9.99/month recurring
#   4. Copy the Price ID (starts with price_)
#   5. Webhooks → Add endpoint: https://yourdomain.com/api/stripe/webhook
#   6. Select events: checkout.session.completed, customer.subscription.deleted
#   7. Copy Webhook Secret (starts with whsec_)
#
# VERCEL DEPLOYMENT:
#   1. Go to https://vercel.com → Import your GitHub repo
#   2. Settings → Environment Variables → Add all variables above
#   3. Deploy!
